{"tid":1776083,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解中共會介意黃色經濟圈??","createTime":"2019-12-09T09:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T12:41:11.000Z","uid":259520,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c85c1fae515c3c3ca85f2a2e63aceaf0b66e14","tid":1776083,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"點解中共會介意黃色經濟圈??<br />\n1) 中共常用手法, 經濟侵略. <br />\n黃色經濟圈明顯影響佢既侵略手法.<br />\n<br />\n2) 轉移資產, 大量中共零售企業,可以將中共貨品轉為美元(增加外匯)<br />\n<br />\n3) 統一商界, 無黃色經濟圈插手,<br />\n咁好多商人在有得無失下,易於歸邊中共.<br />\n(黃色經濟圈做唔做得大, 真係睇市民本身)<br />\n<br />\nremarks: 個人認為,唔好迫商人表態,<br />\n容許佢地只做生意,唔理政治.<br />\n迫商家只會令商家反感.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外有人話唔好用紅衛兵方式鬥中共.<br />\n呢D人唔係on 9,就係鬼.</span></strong><br />\n一句&quot;以己之道,還施彼身&quot;.<br />\n對方係君子,我地當然用君子方法.<br />\n對方擺明PK, 仲講咩野唔好用陰招???"},{"pid":"43fd66abcc54c062f8ea06dc5e40838c7fd0e44d","tid":1776083,"uid":8000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"5毛唔會推呢個<br />\n我推"},{"pid":"2a262979d2ff0d4a4e04f77ec782cf4f494e5d13","tid":1776083,"uid":224281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43fd66abcc54c062f8ea06dc5e40838c7fd0e44d","tid":1776083,"uid":8000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"5毛唔會推呢個<br />\n我推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"我都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8701e88a67c94f8ca83e737bd783779e29257a","tid":1776083,"uid":202228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88da2846e622428631763ae964d326f343a412dc","tid":1776083,"uid":94279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"做大個餅"},{"pid":"6ebaad978669747993bf956e1d685703a8b10185","tid":1776083,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"盡力同化佢哋"},{"pid":"73e6574020f6b4b0f26