，即係由中轉黃，由藍轉黃，甚至再派生其他情況，例如轉左黃再轉返藍，然後香港人幫唔幫襯，都係取決於自己，當然希望大家多幫襯早啲表態<br />\n<br />\n然後擔心偽黃嘅好簡單，乜間間都表面黃嘅時候，佢查水錶都唔知查邊間，下下針住一間就會令大家更反感，為左一間出名黃舖煲到大家咁反感咁樣好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5e22c505e9911e98e461a0081ed570a022523a","tid":1776083,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"佢地最叻就係唔順佢意思就玩杯葛，而家以其人之道還治其人之身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"643f5488454ad2a044d054bd27f5e81917bfc6c8","tid":1776083,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"大力推 極有用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a1513d5428b38f9ce1bf3f06a9df1a2af8c333","tid":1776083,"uid":24006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"所以咪搵熱狗做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9b6bbd520966a4e3ced93fa835717fc14b7197","tid":1776083,"uid":60070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"738e79af7af132b17add1d0ab4adc5b32ba3b9b2","tid":1776083,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9e1662d8ef902b21b4e7012c034c6522a94923cd","tid":1776083,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"藍屍蝕到入骨<br />\n對於眼裏只有錢的藍屍<br />\n藍罷買就係桶中佢個死穴<br />\n不斷試唔同的招才會知道佢哋驚乜！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" c